{"tid":1516266,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[RESPECT] 被捕City學生記者想同香港人講幾句","createTime":"2019-08-29T13:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:23:03.000Z","uid":153905,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b4449f387f2d95f98806f0b38db01a7827a3f78c","tid":1516266,"uid":153905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/387603714763860/posts/1133891743468383/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F387603714763860%2Fposts%2F1133891743468383%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkFuzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=bd2cb062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/387603714763860/posts/1133891743468383/</a><br />\n<br />\n城大編委致香港的公開信：<br />\n<br />\n各位同行、市民，感謝大家連日來的關注和慰問，本報被捕記者現已保釋。本報強烈譴責警方無故拘捕學生記者、向記者業界製造白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n本報特此發出聲明，作為校園媒體，在接近零資源的情況下，仍謹守新聞報導原則，日夜無間、全方位報導事實真相，全力以赴。然而，警方卻以「莫須有」罪名秋後算帳，加上上星期日(25/8)警方試圖將學生媒體和主流媒體分開界定之舉，令人聯想其針對著學生記者的身分，此舉實在令本報不寒而慄。<br />\n<br />\n同學的被捕，代表著新聞自由開始受到挑戰，第四權面臨搖搖欲墜之危。我們質疑警方在記者會上的說法，並就一切對不同傳媒失實的指控予以強烈譴責。我們嚴正要求警方早日還本報記者清白、學會尊重任何媒體。<br />\n<br />\n最後，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「粉身碎骨渾不怕，要留清白在人間。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港城市大學學生會編輯委員會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xe5Wwe9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXe5Wwe9.jpg&h=17dc93d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df850aeb341b2f6e1fff33e88afc3900b3fa407","tid":1516266,"uid":25048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:38:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a616bbb7e3bb1c1fa93ac3ac5391af0f4ab3d510","tid":1516266,"uid":153905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"同學仔加油<img sr